Blaziken (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0256: Combusken
Pokémon
#0258: Mudkip →

Blaziken has been featured on 24 different cards since it debuted in the EX Ruby & Sapphire expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Blaziken cards are normally Fire-type or Fighting-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Blaziken

Blaziken
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
